        <!-- Version 1.0.0 - Initial Release -->
        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.0</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <h2>Initial Release 🎉</h2>
                    <h3>Features</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>✨ Beautiful modern UI with Nohemi typography</li>
                        <li>📚 All 40 Hadith Nawawi with Arabic, English, and Uzbek translations</li>
                        <li>🔍 Powerful search across all languages</li>
                        <li>❤️ Favorites system to mark your preferred hadiths</li>
                        <li>🔔 Daily reminder notifications</li>
                        <li>📍 Menu bar integration for quick access</li>
                        <li>📤 Export to text, markdown, or JSON</li>
                        <li>⌨️ Keyboard shortcuts for efficient navigation</li>
                        <li>🔒 100% private - no data collection</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>System Requirements</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>macOS 14.0 (Sonoma) or later</li>
                        <li>Apple Silicon or Intel Mac</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p><strong>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ</strong></p>
                    <p><em>May Allah accept this humble effort.</em></p>
                ]]>
            </description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>

